===== 2026-04-30

Source file and pdf doc are from Lisa Preble lpreble@uci.edu
put in /data/opt/sources/ANSYS/2025R2

1 untar the source
  cd /data/opt/sources/ANSYS/2025R2
  mkdir untarred
  cd untarred
  gunzip -c ../ FLUIDS_2025R2_LINX64.tgz | tar xvf -

2 run intall command
  mkdir -p /data/opt/apps/fluent/2025R2/
  ./INSTALL -silent -install_dir "/data/opt/apps/fluent/2025R2" -fluent -licserverinfo 2325:1055:128.200.217.34
  
3 Move installation relicts to one place
  cd /data/opt/sources/ANSYS/2025R2
  mv /data/opt/apps/fluent/2025R2/install.log .
  mv /root/.ansys root-dot-ansys
  rm -rf untarred/

Note, license info for the server is provided by Lisa
Install command does installtion of only the fluent app (the tar file provides all ansys apps)

This file is copied to nfsapps-admix repo in yamlspecs/ANSYS/2025R2
